# This directory is a self-contained offline deployment artifact and MUST ship
# its production node_modules — the target server has no internet access.
#
# The root .gitignore excludes `node_modules` everywhere. We override that
# exclusion here, scoped to this directory only. The root .gitignore is
# deliberately not modified.
#
# Re-include both the directory itself and all of its contents (git won't
# look inside a directory that's still excluded, so both lines are required).
!node_modules/
!node_modules/**
